# FileSqueeze Development Policy

## Installation/Uninstallation

**ALWAYS use the provided scripts - NEVER use pip directly**

```powershell
# Install (first time or update)
.\install.ps1

# Reinstall (force reinstall)
.\install.ps1 -Force

# Or use Poetry scripts:
poetry run install
poetry run reinstall
poetry run uninstall
```

**DO NOT** use:
- `pip install filesqueeze` - won't set up shortcuts/config/auto-start
- `pip uninstall filesqueeze` - won't clean up properly

## Project Structure

- `filesqueeze/system/` - Platform abstraction layer (binaries, platform detection, logging)
- `filesqueeze/ops/` - File processing operations (video, pdf, image, presentation)
- `filesqueeze/fsm/` - State machine components
- `install.ps1` / `uninstall.ps1` - Use these for all installation/uninstallation

## Module Imports

After refactor, use these import paths:
- `filesqueeze.system.binaries` - NOT `filesqueeze.binaries`
- `filesqueeze.system.platform` - Platform detection utilities
- `filesqueeze.system.config_adapters` - Config transformation utilities
